### Iegūst visus kursa rezultātus
GET http://localhost:8080/api/course-results
Accept: application/json

###

### Iegūst rezultātu pēc ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/course-results/1267f4dc-9360-44b0-90c3-9ee151753555
Accept: application/json

###

### Iegūst visus rezultātus pēc kursa ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/course-results/by-course/ce8a26aa-79d3-42a1-8711-b8a47745eff3
Accept: application/json

###

### Izveido jaunu kursa rezultātu
POST http://localhost:8080/api/course-results
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "course": {
    "id": "0da561bd-8665-48c2-9a03-2befc1ad1386"
  },
  "category": {
    "id": "1"
  },
  "language": "lv",
  "learningOutcome": "Studējošais zina algoritmus datu analīzē."
}

###

### Atjauno kursa rezultātu
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/course-results/1267f4dc-9360-44b0-90c3-9ee151753555
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "course": {
    "id": "ce8a26aa-79d3-42a1-8711-b8a47745eff3"
  },
  "category": {
    "id": "1"
  },
  "language": "lv",
  "learningOutcome": "Atjaunināts rezultāts ar uzlabotu formulējumu."
}

###

### Dzēš kursa rezultātu
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/course-results/1267f4dc-9360-44b0-90c3-9ee151753555
